<P>
 * Douglas Marney; Theater Managing Director  
</P>
<P>
 Douglas Marney, 42, managing director of Theatre West in Hollywood for the 
last eight years.A native of Montana who grew up in Wyoming, Marney graduated 
summa cum laude in theater arts from the University of Montana. He began his 
career as an actor, working at the Big Fork Summer Playhouse and in musicals 
and classic drama in Cirque Dinner Theater, Skid Row Theater, Pioneer Square 
and other Seattle venues. Switching to administration, he moved to Los Angeles 
and Theatre West as managing director in 1986. On Nov. 23 in Los Angeles after 
a long illness. 
