SEASONAL SPLENDOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Just for a millisecond or two: Forget the election results. 
</P>
<P>
 Forget economics. 
</P>
<P>
 Forget Proposition 187. 
</P>
<P>
 Forget GATT. 
</P>
<P>
 Forget Bosnia. 
</P>
<P>
 Has anyone ever seen Southern California's trees provide a greater display of 
autumn's splendor? 
</P>
<P>
 DON & VI SMITH 
</P>
