<P>
 The Azusa Pacific women's volleyball team will play St. Francis (Ill.) and 
Hastings (Neb.) today in the second day of pool play at the 20-team National 
Assn. of Intercollegiate Athletics championships at Chattanooga, Tenn. 
</P>
<P>
 The Cougars, who entered the tournament with a 22-10 record, opened play 
Wednesday night against St. Vincent (Penn.). Results were not available at 
