 Cancer Society Seeks a Variety of Helpers 
</P>
<P>
 The Irvine branch of the American Cancer Society needs volunteers to help with 
office duties, including answering telephone calls. Volunteers are also needed 
to provide patient transportation and may also work at health fairs and in fund 
raising. For information, call Sally Carson at (714) 751-0441. 
