<HEADLINE>
<P>
METROPOLITAN DIGEST / LOS ANGELES COUNTY NEWS IN BRIEF: LOS ANGELES; METROLINK 
TO RUN SPECIAL HOLIDAY TRAINS DEC. 10, 17 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Metrolink normally is in operation only Monday through Friday, but officials 
announced this week that special Saturday runs will be made on Dec. 10 and 17 
because of the holiday season. 
</P>
<P>
 Metrolink will run trains on Dec. 10 into Los Angeles from Santa Clarita, 
Orange County, San Bernardino and Riverside.  
</P>
<P>
 On Dec. 17, trains will run into Los Angeles from Ventura, San Bernardino and 
Riverside.  
</P>
<P>
 Metrolink also ran special holiday trains in 1993 and 1992.  
</P>
<P>
 The special weekend fare will be $5 regardless of the distance traveled. 
Passengers with a December monthly pass or a validated 10-trip ticket can ride 
at no additional cost. For ticket information call (213) 626-7259. 
</P>
</TEXT>
