 After he was shot, the man -- described by acquaintances as about 20 years old 
-- staggered down the street toward Herrera Bakery, said Frank Herrera, whose 
mother called police. 
</P>
<P>
 "My parents heard the gunshot," Herrera said. "My mom went out, but all she 
saw was him on the floor." 
