<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 1, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 1; Column 1; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
