 EDISON 03,17,09,08 1993-94 RECORDS OVERALL LEAGUE 17-9 8-6 02,12,18 COACH 
RECORD AT SCHOOL Dave White 142-49 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. HGT. P 
Kim Bartling Sr. 6-1 C Becky Loshak Jr. 5-8 G Kerry O'Bric Jr. 5-8 G Marie 
Philman Jr. 6-0 F Danielle Wiggins Sr. 5-8 G 04,20,05,06,04 TOP RETURNERS YR. 
