<HEADLINE>
<P>
DIGEST; HERNANDEZ ENROLLS AT VALLEY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By FERNANDO DOMINGUEZ 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Zack Hernandez, a former L.A. Baptist quarterback who redshirted at Cal 
Lutheran this season, has enrolled for the spring semester at Valley College, 
Monarch football Coach Jim Fenwick said Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Hernandez passed for 3,634 yards and 26 touchdowns his senior season at L.A. 
Baptist in 1993. FERNANDO DOMINGUEZ 
</P>
</TEXT>
