<TEXT>
<P>
 High school football -- Because of a reporter's error, linebacker Jon Gibbs of 
Agoura High was inadvertently omitted from a list of the Marmonte League award 
winners in Wednesday's editions. He was named Marmonte League lineman of the 
year. 
</P>
